# Local-only working docs — superpowers brainstorming, design rounds,
# codex review findings. Mirrors the djogi convention.
docs/superpowers/

# Rust build artifacts. `target/` (not `/target`) covers both the
# workspace target dir and the per-crate `<crate>/target/` directories
# that `cargo lihaaf --manifest-path <crate>/Cargo.toml` creates when
# the harness builds against a sub-crate manifest.
target/

